Topic: troubleshoot

Troubleshooting

No search results:
  Try fewer keywords, remove restrictive `--type` filters, or inspect the archive with:
    wikigraph <archive-uri> index

Missing generated objects:
  Queue the relevant generation task for the chapter:
    wikigraph <chapter-uri> queue add --task reading-graph --accept-cost
    wikigraph <chapter-uri> queue add --task reading-summary --accept-cost

Need machine-readable output:
  Use `--json` or `--jsonl` on object commands.
